ed="T" n="0720a14"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0720a14"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000023662">洛京天竺寺</placeName><persName key="A001922">寶思惟</persName>傳<ptr target="#n183"/></head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0720a15"/><persName key="A001922">釋阿儞真那</persName><ptr target="#n184"/>，<name>華</name>言<persName key="A001922">寶思惟</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000055417">北印度迦濕<anchor xml:id="beg0720001"/>密<anchor xml:id="end0720001"/><lb
ed="T" n="0720a16"/>羅國</placeName>人，剎帝利<ptr type="glossary" target="#g361"/>種。幼而捨家，禪誦為業。進<lb
ed="T" n="0720a17"/>具之後，專精律品，而慧解超群，學兼真俗。<lb
ed="T" n="0720a18"/>乾文<ptr type="glossary" target="#g362"/>、呪術，尤攻其妙。加以化導為心，無戀<lb
ed="T" n="0720a19"/>鄉國。以<persName key="A002099">天后</persName><date from-iso="+0692-12-17" key="j19741591974512" to-iso="+0693-12-05"><name>長壽</name>二年</date>，屆于<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛都</placeName>，勅於<placeName key="PL000000023564">天<lb
ed="T" n="0720a20"/>宮寺</placeName>安置。即以<date from-iso="+0692-12-17" key="j19741591979326" to-iso="+0707-02-10">其年創譯至<name>中宗</name><name>神龍</name>景<lb
ed="T" n="0720a21"/>午</date>，於<placeName key="PL000000023657">佛授記</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000023564">天宮</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000023665">福先</placeName>等寺出《不空罥索陀<lb
ed="T" n="0720a22"/>羅尼經》等七部<ptr target="#n363"/>。<persName key="A002461">睿宗</persName><date from-iso="+0712-05-14" key="j19812461981275" to-iso="+0712-06-12"><name><anchor xml:id="beg0720002"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>大</sic><corr>太</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0720002"/>極</name>元年四月</date>，太子洗<lb
ed="T" n="0720a23"/>馬<persName key="A000442">張齊賢</persName>等繕寫進內。<date from-iso="+0712-07-13" key="j19813061981334" to-iso="+0712-08-10">其年六月</date>，勅令禮部<lb
ed="T" n="0720a24"/>尚書<name>晉國公</name><persName key="A009028">薛稷</persName>、右常侍高平侯<persName key="A009029">徐彥伯</persName>等<lb
ed="T" n="0720a25"/>詳定<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g364"/>入目施行。<persName key="A001922">那</persName>自<date from-iso="+0705-02-25" key="j19786111979566" to-iso="+0707-10-08"><name>神龍</name></date>之後，不務翻譯，<lb
ed="T" n="0720a26"/>唯精勤<anchor xml:id="beg0720sgsz1"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0720sgsz1"/>誦，修諸福業。每於晨朝磨香為<lb
ed="T" n="0720a27"/>水，塗浴佛像<ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n365"/>，後方飲食。從始洎終，此為恒<lb
ed="T" n="0720a28"/>業。衣鉢之外，隨得隨施。後於<placeName key="PL000000023647">龍門山</placeName>請置<lb
ed="T" n="0720a29"/>一寺，制度皆依<placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName>，因名「天竺」焉。門徒學<pb ed="T" n="0720b" xml:id="T50.2061.0720b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0720b01"/>侶同居<ref target="#PL000000023662" type="place">此寺</ref>，精誠所感，靈應寔繁。壽百有餘<lb
ed="T" n="0720b02"/>歲，以<date from-iso="+0721-02-05" key="j19844351984789" to-iso="+0722-01-25"><name>開元</name>九年</date>終於<ref target="#PL000000023662" type="place">寺</ref>，構塔旌表焉。</p>
